import React from 'react'
import { 
    ContactContainer, 
    ContactMeTitle,
    ContactH5,
    FirstNameInput 
} from './ContactElements'

const Contact = () => {
  return (
    <ContactContainer>
        <ContactTitleContainer>
            <ContactMeTitle>
                CONTACT
            </ContactMeTitle>
            <ContactH5>
                Available for work. Get in touch.
            </ContactH5>
        </ContactTitleContainer>
        <FirstNameInput></FirstNameInput>
    </ContactContainer>
  )
}

export default Contact
